Class AvaiableCountryView

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class AvaiableCountryView
extends BaseView
    This is view which display country table and country form. Logic is that if you choose some country from country table then you can edit it in form. If no then you can create the new one. See AvaiableCountryController for more information about logic.
    Since:
    1.0.0.
    Author:
    Martin Tomasek (martin@toms-cz.com)
